<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>html forms</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Forms In HTML</h1>

<p>this is my forms homework</p>

<hr>

<form>

name:
<br>
<input type="text">

<br><br>

password:
<br>
<input type="password">

<br><br>

email:
<br>
<input type="email">

<br><br>

age:
<br>
<input type="number">

<br><br>

birthday:
<br>
<input type="date">

<br><br>

gender:
<br>

<input type="radio" name="a"> male

<br>

<input type="radio" name="a"> female

<br><br>

what do you learn?

<br>

<input type="checkbox"> html

<br>

<input type="checkbox"> css

<br>

<input type="checkbox"> js

<br><br>

choose your major

<br>

<select>

<option>IT</option>
<option>CS</option>
<option>AI</option>

</select>

<br><br>

write something:

<br>

<textarea rows="4" cols="20"></textarea>

<br><br>

<input type="submit">

<input type="reset">

</form>

</body>
</html>
